<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV18">
<l>kaṭalkoṇ ṭeḻuntatu vāṉamav vāṉattai yaṉṟicceṉṟu</l>
<l>kaṭalkoṇ ṭeḻunta vataṉā litukaṇṇaṉ maṇṇumviṇṇuṅ</l>
<l>kaṭalkoṇ ṭeḻuntavak kālaṅko lōpuyaṟ kālaṅkolō</l>
<l>kaṭalkoṇṭa kaṇṇī raruvicey yāniṟkuṅ kārikaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The cloud has risen from the ocean. The oceans have risen, going</l>
<l>[and] taking not only that cloud. Therefore, is this that time when the ocean</l>
<l>takes Kaṇṇaṉ’s earth and sky [and] rises or is it the time of raining,</l>
<l>oh woman who keeps making tear waterfalls one might take for the ocean?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
